    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2 class="h4">Professional Focus</h2>
        <p>
            I build practical systems with an emphasis on reliability, maintainability, and fast iteration.
            This site highlights current work and serves as a stable landing page for future portfolio content.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2 class="h4">What You'll Find Here</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Current project portfolio with placeholders for upcoming write-ups</li>
            <li>Hosted resume PDF and quick download access</li>
            <li>Community links for Dorks & Dice</li>
            <li>Contact routes for professional outreach</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
